{"type":"text","timestamp":1775861519261,"sessionID":"ses_28669cebaffeZdBF8wDXlUi4gG","part":{"id":"prt_d79982ed700178NGzTn3Gz2NZZ","messageID":"msg_d7997fa81001UVkGAhphA6f27l","sessionID":"ses_28669cebaffeZdBF8wDXlUi4gG","type":"text","text":"## Verification Result: **NOT IMPLEMENTED**\n\nThe client-go library specified in `deployment/client-go.md` is **completely missing** from the codebase.\n\n### Findings:\n\n| Spec Requirement | Status | Evidence |\n|-----------------|--------|----------|\n| `client-go/` directory | **MISSING** | Directory does not exist |\n| `clientset/versioned/clientset.go` | **MISSING** | No clientset files |\n| Typed clients (`agentruntime.go`, `codeinterpreter.go`) | **MISSING** | Not generated |\n| Informers (`externalversions/`) | **MISSING** | Not generated |\n| Listers (`listers/runtime/v1alpha1/`) | **MISSING** | Not generated |\n| Fake clients | **MISSING** | Not generated |\n| `hack/update-codegen.sh` | **MISSING** | No hack directory |\n| `make gen-client` target | **MISSING** | No Makefile |\n| API types with markers | **IMPLEMENTED** | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` exists with correct `+genclient` markers |\n\n### API Types Status (Partial):\n- `AgentRuntime`/`AgentRuntimeList`: ✅ Correct `+genclient`, `+kubebuilder:object:root=true`, `+kubebuilder:subresource:status` markers\n- `CodeInterpreter`/`CodeInterpreterList`: ✅ Same markers present\n- `SchemeGroupVersion`: ✅ Correctly set to `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`\n- `zz_generated.deepcopy.go`: ✅ Exists\n\n### Tests:\n- `pkg/store` tests fail (Valkey connectivity issue - unrelated to this spec)\n- Other packages pass\n\n### Conclusion:\nThe spec requires a generated client-go library at module path `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go` with clientsets, typed clients, informers, listers, and fake clients. None of this exists. The workloadmanager currently uses `dynamic.Interface` instead of the typed clients that should have been generated.","time":{"start":1775861